OBX|1|TX|24690-0^US Retroperitoneal Complete^LN|1|CLINICAL INDICATION: F/U right complex renal cyst.||||||F
OBX|2|FT|24690-0^US Retroperitoneal Complete^LN|2|FINDINGS: COMPARISON:  CT scan of 6/18/07 and renal ultrasound 8/25/07.\.br\\.br\FINDINGS:  On today's examination, both kidneys appear to be of\.br\normal size, shape and echogenicity.  No masses or cystic lesions\.br\are identified in either kidney.  There is no hydronephrosis\.br\involving either kidney.\.br\\.br\Particular attention was paid to the area in the right kidney\.br\where the finding was located and no abnormalities are seen on\.br\today's examination.\.br\\.br\** IMPRESSION **:\.br\Negative renal ultrasound.||||||F
